{"tid":1901974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★勞福局建議2月起綜援生果金調高3.6%","createTime":"2020-02-28T06:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T08:00:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a230aa749a776b5e5d2e2bb0f38e42db5726a08a","tid":1901974,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局今日（10日）向財委會提交文件，建議下月1日起把綜援計劃的標準項目金額及公共福利金計劃的高齡津貼、長者生活津貼和傷殘津貼金額調 高3.6%；而綜援租金津貼最高金額亦上調3.2%。政府預計每年額外增加逾27億元財政負擔，有關建議留待財委會下周五（17日）審批。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/420361/%E5%8B%9E%E7%A6%8F%E5%B1%80%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B02%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E7%94%9F%E6%9E%9C%E9%87%91%E8%AA%BF%E9%AB%983-6-%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F420361%2F%25E5%258B%259E%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B02%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25B6%259C%25E6%258F%25B4%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259E%259C%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E9%25AB%25983-6-%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%2589%25B9&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0UzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=cbea52e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/420361/%E5%8B%9E%E7%A6%8F%E5%B1%80%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B02%E6%9C%88%E8%B5%B7%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E7%94%9F%E6%9E%9C%E9%87%91%E8%AA%BF%E9%AB%983-6-%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9</a>"},{"pid":"63539a1694a8b3abd509f6b03be3a1b64e0b6ae5","tid":1901974,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"fb55b32e876f9a973cb21a99fd237e7b4f768286","tid":1901974,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid